## Topic 12: Inference Practice

###

In the Topic 11 workbook you learned more about statistical inference (in the form of hypothesis tests and confidence intervals) for categorical variables. In this workbook we'll continue where we left off at the end of Topic 11. You'll start with a video explaining the [*Standard Error Decision Tree*](www/StdErrorDecisionTree.pdf){target="_blank"}, and then move on to a few practice problems with the opportunity to view a few worked solutions if you need some help! Make sure to try the problems and mark down the questions you have.

## A Tour of the Decision Tree

From this point on you'll make heavy use of the [*Standard Error Decision Tree*](www/StdErrorDecisionTree.pdf){target="_blank"} that was referenced earlier. The tree may look intimidating for now, but it contains almost everything we'll need to get through the majority of what remains in our course. Let's start with a tour.

###

